OL,3,C'Undervalued' Guernsey civil servants
OL,4,Creject 5% pay offer
OL,6,FGuernsey civil servants have rejected
OL,7,Fa 5% pay offer in the first such
OL,8,Fdispute for more than 20 years.
OL,10,FThe Association of Guernsey Civil
OL,11,FServants, which is associated with the
OL,12,Ftrade union Prospect, says its members
OL,13,Fmade the "unprecedented decision" due
OL,14,Fto cost of living pressures, pay not
OL,15,Fkeeping up with inflation and wider
OL,16,Ffrustrations over increasing workloads
OL,17,F"without the investment in resources".
