OL,3,C'Undervalued' Guernsey civil servants
OL,4,Creject 5% pay offer
OL,6,FThe group adds: "The States is asking
OL,7,Fits workers to do more with less and
OL,8,Fdespite their efforts to maintain
OL,9,Fservices at an acceptable standard,
OL,10,Fall too often civil servants in
OL,11,Fparticular are being unfairly and very
OL,12,Fpublicly criticised and disrespected
OL,13,Ffor their efforts.
OL,15,F"This has seriously affected wellbeing
OL,16,Fand morale and is inexcusable.
