OL,3,C'Undervalued' Guernsey civil servants
OL,4,Creject 5% pay offer
OL,6,FIn response, Deputy John Gollop from
OL,7,FPolicy and Resources says: "Given the
OL,8,Ffact the Budget hasn't been entirely
OL,9,Ffunded and we await the introduction
OL,10,Fof GST, we thought it was a good offer
OL,11,Fand it has been accepted, potentially
OL,12,Freluctantly, by another set of workers.
OL,14,F"I am disappointed that from a
OL,15,Fcorporate perspective we aren't all on
OL,16,Fthe same horizon. There has been
OL,17,Frestraint in public sector
OL,18,Fexpenditure. However, I believe we do
OL,19,Fhave a duty to the taxpayer to ensure
OL,20,Frequests for pay increases aren't
OL,21,Fonerous."
